<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.248820>
    dc:description "FIGURE 42. Colour variation of M. maxillosa. A, Form I, male, Sumatra. B, Form I, female, Borneo. C, Form II, male, Borneo. D, Form II, female, Borneo. E, Form III, male, Sumatra. F, Form III, female, Borneo. (B, C and F were collected from the same sites in Borneo) (Scales. A – F: 1 mm / division)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/248820/files/figure.png" ;
